{
  "title": "ReFi Roundup #16: Terra collapse, ReFi Portugal & Earth Day Hackathon Retro!",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-16",
  "html": "<h3 id=\"hello-refi-peeps%F0%9F%91%8B-jeremy-here-with-my-first-edition-of-the-roundup-im-a-serial-entrepreneur-with-a-passion-for-regeneration-currently-im-working-on-a-project-called-resource-that-is-pioneering-on-chain-regenerative-villages-in-portugal\">Hello ReFi peeps!ğŸ‘‹ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jeremyanew\">Jeremy</a> here with my first edition of the Roundup. I'm a serial entrepreneur with a passion for regeneration. Currently, I'm working on a project called Re:Source that is pioneering on-chain regenerative villages in Portugal.</h3><p>Many thanks to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto\">jE</a> for editorial support and fleshing out some of the narrative!</p><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-purple\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">ğŸ’¡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\">It's an exciting time to be a part of the ReFi movement - if you have a story you want included in next week's roundup, submit a story below!</div></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://tally.so/r/3jOz1w\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Submit a story</a></div><h1 id=\"terra-ponzi-collapse\">Terra Ponzi collapse </h1><p>It seems some stable coins arenâ€™t as stable as they are supposed to be, casting doubt across the whole crypto space. The big takeaway here is that <em>not all stablecoins are created equally.</em> </p><p>Yet another algorithmic stable coin experiment has failed, this time causing over $90B in losses in just under a week. This triggered a broader market meltdown with losses across the board.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Lehman Brothers was a 60bn market cap company that went down... <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24LUNA&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$LUNA</a> is a 50bn at the top plus 30bn TVL on UST. To give you guys context how massive this event is. This is a big event in the financial markets. Majority of the people takin the hit are retail.</p>&mdash; Wizard Of SoHo (ğŸ·,ğŸ·) (@wizardofsoho) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wizardofsoho/status/1524281371027517442?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 11, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Our hearts go out to everyone who lost money in this process. If you or anyone you know is suffering, please feel free to reach out! We're a community that cares and are always happy to listen or put you in touch with experts who can help.</p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FqW4-FGA9j4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe><figcaption><a href=\"http://podcast.banklesshq.com/\" rel=\"\">Listen to podcast episode</a> | <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/bankless/id1499409058\" rel=\"\">Apple</a> | <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/41TNnXSv5ExcQSzEGLlGhy\" rel=\"\">Spotify</a> | <a href=\"https://youtu.be/FqW4-FGA9j4\" rel=\"\">YouTube</a></figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"wtf-happened\">WTF happened?</h2><p>TerraUSD (USDT) and its sister coin LUNA suffered a 99.9% drop in just under seven days... The mass market sell off also exposed the Cosmos ecosystem and had serious ripple effects across the entire crypto market. This happened as a result of several factors:</p><ol><li>USDT was a grossly under-collateralized stable coin.</li><li>The Luna Foundation Guard (LFG) began buying Bitcoin to provide collateral to mitigate the risk of USDT losing it's peg</li><li>USDT had reduced liquidity as a result of the migration to a 4pool Curve liquidity pool, designed to 'win the curve wars'</li><li>USDT and Luna had grown explosively through the unsustainable 20% yield offered by Anchor protocol.</li><li>Anchor reduced it's yield and as <a href=\"https://forum.makerdao.com/t/ust-update-terra/14230/13\">many predicted</a>, triggered a huge sell off of UST.</li><li>Additionally, a trader (or attackerâ€”if you wish), borrowed 100k Bitcoin and bought over 1B of USDT directly from the LFG and proceeded to sell USDT in large chunks, beginning with a 350M sale on Curve, followed by 200k - 5M sales on Binance</li><li>USDT lost it's peg and forced the LFG to sell off it's Bitcoin reserves to try and buy back USDT. </li><li>This triggered massive sell-off across the Terra ecosystem, with many redeeming USDT for LUNA and selling for exit.</li><li>Many retail investors got rekt as most institutional funds were able to exit in time.</li></ol><p>For a deeper dive, check out <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BenGiove\">Ben Giove</a>'s analysis on Bankless.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://newsletter.banklesshq.com/p/ust-luna-meltdown-what-happened?s&#x3D;w\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">UST Luna Meltdown: What Happened?</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">A post-mortem on cryptoâ€™s biggest collapse</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/54ddfd59-2bad-4546-b7f7-ea5ef6ba7829/apple-touch-icon-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Bankless</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Ben Giove</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca8bb4c1-9d5e-4492-bc60-7c6c96fceb70_2668x1501.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/f63479367e5e12b966ae728c9db00064/tenor.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"498\" height=\"498\"></figure><h2 id=\"crypto-winter-%F0%9F%A5%B6\">Crypto winter ğŸ¥¶</h2><p>Overall, the entire crypto market has been slashed by more than half since November, falling to $1.2 trillion from $2.9 trillion, according to data from CoinMarketCap.</p><p>As a result of the Luna crash landing, the ReFi space got hit harder this week with impact related chains like Regen who saw a 35% drop. IXO was down a massive 64%, Celo fell by 38% and Toucan protocolâ€™s BCT dropped 13%. </p><p>DAOs like Klima, Gitcoin, EarthFund and Popcorn took a hard tumble between 30-50%.</p><p>ReFi Twitter seems to hope that as the lessons emerge from the LUNA disaster, we could see a positive shift for ReFiâ€”as investors choose to deploy their capital into currencies backed by tangible assets instead. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Reminded of our conversation in Episode 5 with Markus Franke from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CeloOrg</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/cLabs?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@cLabs</a> about using nature to back currencies.<br><br>How might the stable coins of the future look if land is a primary collateral asset?<br><br>Listen: <a href=\"https://t.co/9UN94FTLsA\">https://t.co/9UN94FTLsA</a><br>Watch: <a href=\"https://t.co/ZoHh1dZTog\">https://t.co/ZoHh1dZTog</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/HbqGSeyNb6\">pic.twitter.com/HbqGSeyNb6</a></p>&mdash; ReFi Podcast (@ReFiPodcast) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiPodcast/status/1525834686173519875?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 15, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h1 id=\"natural-capital-backed-currencies\">Natural capital backed currencies</h1><p>Despite the shock of the collapse of the Terra ecosystem, there is a trend emerging in established stablecoin communities like <a href=\"https://forum.makerdao.com/\">Maker DAO</a> and <a href=\"https://forum.celo.org/\">Celo</a> as well as up and coming projects like <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ECORISEDAO\">Ecorise</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Kumo_DAO\">Kumo DAO</a> looking to create stablecoins backed by natural capital assets.</p><p>In the case of Terraâ€”imagine if their community had decided to aggressively buy forests at risk of degradation in order to back their stable coin?</p><p>Land tends to be a less correlated asset to the broader crypto market and provides real world value.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://forum.makerdao.com/t/the-case-for-clean-money/10684/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">The case for Clean Money</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Clean Money MakerDAO is in the position to use the most powerful tool ever invented to fight the most challenging problem ever faced - all it takes is the will of a community. With the Maker Foundation dissolving, Iâ€™ve had a chance to reflect on the future of the project. We have come incredibly faâ€¦</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://makerdao-forum-backup.s3.dualstack.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/optimized/1X/68e5b859631b8f66624f5880acb8c189a32aee64_2_180x180.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">The Maker Forum</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">rune</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://makerdao-forum-backup.s3.dualstack.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/optimized/2X/2/2bcf59e14092beae70a4c838103811c106ca75ce_2_1024x505.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://www.ledgerinsights.com/celo-hopes-to-invest-stablecoin-asset-backing-in-rainforests/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Celo hopes to invest $340m stablecoin asset backing in rainforests - Ledger Insights - enterprise blockchain</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Celo is proposing to use 40% of the assets that back its stablecoins to invest in rainforests. Itâ€™s launching the Climate Collective</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Ledger Insights - enterprise blockchain</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Ledger Insights</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://www.ledgerinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/rain-forest.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/05/ReFiSpring-Event-Header-TDF.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/05/ReFiSpring-Event-Header-TDF.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/05/ReFiSpring-Event-Header-TDF.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/05/ReFiSpring-Event-Header-TDF.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"refi-portugal-may-26\">ReFi Portugal May 26</h2><p>ReFi Portugal is hosting a ReFi Spring event on May 26 at the <a href=\"https://traditionaldreamfactory.com/\">Traditional Dream Factory</a>, a pioneering regenerative village where Regens can learn about the application of ReFi protocols in a real-world context. They're combining communities of on the ground regeneration with web3 experts.</p><p>We're expecting this to be a real celebration of hope and human ingenuity. You can read more and <a href=\"https://spring.refidao.com/events/refi-spring-portugal-1\">buy your tickets here</a>.</p><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-accent\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-bites\">ReFi Bites</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"a-smattering-of-whats-been-twittered\">A smattering of whats been twittered</h3></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/YahooNews?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@YahooNews</a> covered our partnership with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CeloOrg</a>!<br><br>~Celo Foundation and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Climate?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Climate</a> Collective to purchase at least $10M worth of GNT and support liquidity for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/carbon?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#carbon</a> trading on CeloğŸ’š<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/sustainable?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#sustainable</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CarbonNeutral?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CarbonNeutral</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/decarbonization?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#decarbonization</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NetZero?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NetZero</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/zhgg0mvyin\">https://t.co/zhgg0mvyin</a></p>&mdash; Flowcarbon (@weareflowcarbon) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/weareflowcarbon/status/1524766953637920768?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 12, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"celo-flow-carbon-partner-for-gnt-launch\">Celo + Flow Carbon Partner for GNT Launch</h2><p><a href=\"https://celo.org/\">Celo Foundation</a> and <a href=\"https://climatecollective.org/\">Climate Collective</a> have agreed to purchase at least $10M worth of <a href=\"https://www.flowcarbon.com/\">Flow Carbon</a>'s Goddess Nature Token (GNT) and support liquidity for carbon trading on Celo.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Celo Camp happening Now! ğŸ˜<a href=\"https://t.co/CgqVLRrEhq\">https://t.co/CgqVLRrEhq</a></p>&mdash; Celo (@CeloOrg) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg/status/1525667423935836160?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 15, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"celo-camp-batch-5-kicking-off\">Celo Camp Batch 5 Kicking Off!</h2><p>Meet the 30 impressive teams, including several members of the ReFi DAO community: <a href=\"https://closer.earth/\">Closer</a>, <a href=\"https://athena.tech/\">Aethena Protocol</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ClimateGuards\">Climate Guardians</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.flowcarbon.com/\">Flowcarbon</a>.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/celoorg/celo-camp-batch-5-teams-announced-68eced4807d5\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read more</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/41cYlU-h_4Oca3ZE03LA0hSiCCfm2tkGyPKZJ23qaYpX5Ne5fYYyOBogaV_sO841xnWlImhOPO7kNplTL7Ds75dDQ86EhQ1h5eiFgd5n35Fc9Y5Ta-Ald4v2XP57NWN904UiN5RnHFDtjJuM6g\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></figure><h2 id=\"pozzle-planet-astr0-0nfts\">Pozzle Planet Astr0 0NFTs </h2><p>Pozzle Planet announces the â€˜Astr0 Zer0sâ€™ NFT collection, <a href=\"https://pozzleplanet.medium.com/astr0s-the-first-omnichain-nft-protocol-drop-808e9b64bf0d\">described as the first utility NFT on Layer0 with IPY</a>. It allows for token launches to reduce token selling pressure and solves liquidity for the early investor, while Astr0s contain unique properties by embedding bonuses into the NFTs.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ğŸ’¢ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ECORISEDAO?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ECORISEDAO</a>  has decided to postpone the launch of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24RISE&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$RISE</a> token on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TrustSwap?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TrustSwap</a> <br><br>ğŸ’¢ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ECORISE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ECORISE</a> is currently in discussions with multiple top 10 exchanges regarding the possibility of listing the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24RISE&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$RISE</a> token post-launch<br><br>ğŸ”½ INFO<a href=\"https://t.co/WgdKLSM5X2\">https://t.co/WgdKLSM5X2</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DeFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#DeFi</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Definews?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Definews</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/RISE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#RISE</a></p>&mdash; ğŸŒ ğƒğ„ğ…ğˆ ğğ„ğ–ğ’ ğŸŒ (@Definews_Info) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Definews_Info/status/1523542468100501505?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 9, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"ecorise-rise-token-launch-postponed\">Ecorise $RISE token launch postponed</h2><p>â€‹â€‹As featured in our last ReFi Roundup, the Ecorise $RISE token launch has had to be <a href=\"https://medium.com/@EcoriseDAO/rise-token-launch-postponed-1dd918106b01\">delayed in light of the recent crash</a>.</p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The on-chain carbon market is growing rapidly - to date, almost 22m carbon credits have been bridged ğŸš€ <br><br>But innovation calls for constant iteration. We&#39;ve taken important steps to ensure raising standards in the on-chain carbon market.<br><br>Here&#39;s what we did<br>A ğŸ§µ ğŸ‘‡</p>&mdash; Toucan Protocol (@ToucanProtocol) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol/status/1524740390401634304?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 12, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"toucan-provides-major-bct-upgrade\">Toucan Provides Major BCT Upgrade</h2><p>Toucan has <a href=\"https://t.co/Wmxr6E0Kns\">taken important steps</a> to improve the integrity of on-chain credits in the Base Carbon Tonne (BCT) pool. Each credit now needs to have &lt;10 years between the vintage year and the issuance of the resulting carbon credit.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/raising-standards-in-the-on-chain-carbon-market/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Raising standards in the on-chain carbon market</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Toucan is adding additional safeguards to improve the integrity of on-chain credits.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/favicon.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Toucan Protocol</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Anna Watson</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/content/images/2022/05/blog_BCT-delta_1375.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ğŸ“£Â BICOWG Squad News : <br><br>The working group members have independently and jointly submitted public comments for consideration by the OSTP ğŸ“. <a href=\"https://t.co/iIlNNpWaM7\">https://t.co/iIlNNpWaM7</a></p>&mdash; BICOWG (@BICOWG) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BICOWG/status/1524087849804570625?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 10, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"bicowg-white-house-public-comment\">BICOWG + White House Public Comment</h2><p>The White House made a formal request for info on the Climate Implications of Digital Assets, and The Blockchain Infrastructure Carbon Offset Working Group (<a href=\"https://bicowg.org/\">BICOWG</a>) responded <a href=\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2022/05/09/2438897/0/en/Blockchain-Based-Climate-Impact-Projects-Respond-to-White-House-Office-of-Science-and-Technology-Policy-Request-for-Information-on-Climate-Implications-of-Digital-Assets.html\">making calls</a> for new positively reinforcing regulation for refi, alongside active support and open dialogue with expert advisory. This is the first time the nascent #ReFi industry engages directly with federal policymaking. </p><hr><h2 id=\"solid-world-23m-funding\">Solid World $2.3M Funding! </h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/solidworlddao\">SolidWorldDAO</a> has secured $2.3 million in funding to build pools for pre-purchasing carbon credits. They utilise blockchain technology to tokenize carbon credit pre-purchase agreements.</p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"__GHOST_URL__/planet-positive-nft-hackathon/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Earth Day Retro: Planet Positive NFT Hackathon</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">The planet positive NFT hackathon was a week-long event with $20,000 in bounties. It was a global virtual event that focused on collaboration to address a handful of challenges set by sponsors.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/favicon.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">ReFi Roundup</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Jeremy Agnew</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/01/twitter-01@2x.png\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><h2 id=\"earth-day-retro-planet-positive-nft-hackathon\">Earth Day Retro: Planet Positive NFT Hackathon</h2><p>The <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/planet-positive-nft-hackathon/\">planet positive NFT hackathon </a>was a week-long event with $20,000 in bounties. It was a global virtual event that focused on collaboration to address a handful of challenges set by sponsors.</p><p>In last week's <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-round-up-15/\">ReFi Roundup</a>, we gave a snapshot of the ReFi DAO NFT Hackathon. Today, we wanted to take time to do a little retrospective and share in greater detail what happened, how it worked and why the story of planet positive NFTs is so important for addressing climate change.</p><hr><h2 id=\"submit-a-story\">Submit a story</h2><p>We crowdsource stories from across ReFi, so let us know of any news or announcements in your side of the movement!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe src=\"https://tally.so/embed/3jOz1w?hideTitle=1&alignLeft=1\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" title=\"Tally Forms\"></iframe></figure><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>",
